We are pretty much worthless at level 42, I know that much  <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0">  Sometimes I can help IF there are no archers hiding to snipe us, IF there are no Bards with a long $*#(& range mez, and IF there are no Eldritches with the 928 dmg bolt.  I get a mez off now and then, usually just before I get hit with a bolt. <P>If you get a pet, try to get something small.  I thought it was nice having one of those big kittys, but it just screams 'Hey target me!  If you get me with AOE you'll get the sorcerer too!'<P>--------------------<P>Malachai Mindbender<BR>Enigmatic of Avalon - Guinivere<BR>Sanguis Societat<BR>http://www.farrout.net/sanguis/memberlist.asp?memberID=8
